Decoration is also a problem

12
00:02:13,940 --> 00:02:14,440
And

13
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:17,380
it must be flowers

14
00:02:18,220 --> 00:02:19,940
Your mother loves flowers best

15
00:02:20,860 --> 00:02:23,220
Dad, I will do all these things as you mentioned

16
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:25,260
