39
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,500
I shouldn't trust her

40
00:03:54,340 --> 00:03:56,820
Don't you think Zhuzi is kind of strange recently?

41
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:57,940
She is always strange

42
