50
00:04:17,140 --> 00:04:18,660
How do you like it?

51
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,780
My father said she loved flowers

52
00:04:20,900 --> 00:04:21,620
In this way

53
00:04:21,820 --> 00:04:22,980
We can place more flowers

54
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:26,420
