I have promised him

63
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:11,780
You want to rent my place, right?

64
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:12,980
That's fine

65
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:14,820
But give me some time

66
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:16,460
