74
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:14,900
Xinrang and I were looking for a place these days

75
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:17,140
But we couldn't find a right one

76
00:06:17,860 --> 00:06:21,140
Finally we find that here is a best place

77
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:26,940
It's late

78
00:06:27,220 --> 00:06:28,380
They are still waiting for me at home

79
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:30,780
And lots of things about the wedding need to be done

80
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:33,380
So I gotta go now

81
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:34,780
Let me drive you home

82
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:38,100
Thank you, but I can go home myself

83
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:58,260
By the way

84
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:04,660
If I need your help with problems on the wedding

85
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:07,660
