86
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:14,020
Of course not

87
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:18,300
Thank you

88
00:08:09,860 --> 00:08:11,940
Dear, I'm back

89
00:08:18,780 --> 00:08:20,300
You are back

90
00:08:26,660 --> 00:08:27,420
Dear

91
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:35,420
Dear

92
00:08:43,660 --> 00:08:44,620
Don't cry, dear

93
00:08:45,100 --> 00:08:47,100
Don't cry

94
00:08:49,100 --> 00:08:50,300
Tell me what happened

95
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:55,340
Don't cry

96
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,100
Listen

97
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:58,820
I don't want

98
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:02,260
I don't want romance and anything else

99
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,500
I just want you

100
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:08,380
Don't leave me behind, ok?

101
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:20,060
Are you sure?

102
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:20,960
I'm sure

103
