According to his blood test and other reports

104
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:25,900
I'm basically sure he is good

105
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:29,300
As to why he got such a pathology result

106
00:09:29,700 --> 00:09:32,340
I think there may be some mistakes during his physical examination

107
00:09:44,620 --> 00:09:45,120
Dear

108
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,060
Actually

109
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:04,820
Actually I don't mean to hide it from you

110
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:06,340
Are you ill?

111
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:09,740
I'm alright

112
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:12,900
Really, I'm aright

113
00:10:13,220 --> 00:10:14,180
Tell me

114
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:16,260
What happened to you?

115
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:18,900
What on earth happened to you?

116
00:10:23,620 --> 00:10:25,580
What on earth happened to you?

117
00:10:34,140 --> 00:10:35,380
I'm alright

118
00:10:36,820 --> 00:10:37,700
Just tell me

119
00:10:41,580 --> 00:10:43,700
Tell me what happened to you

120
00:10:48,820 --> 00:10:49,320
Tell me

121
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:57,980
Dear, there is one thing

122
00:11:02,260 --> 00:11:03,500
I want you to know

123
00:11:09,300 --> 00:11:09,800
I

124
00:11:20,660 --> 00:11:21,220
Hello

125
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:23,300
I have got your report

126
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:26,340
I suggest you to get a physical examination again

127
00:11:28,780 --> 00:11:29,660
