128
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:40,620
Thank you

129
00:11:47,940 --> 00:11:49,100
Then what's the result?

130
00:11:50,260 --> 00:11:51,980
Of course it's happy ending

131
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:55,900
The hospital mistook the pathology results

132
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:57,900
Yuan Lang is good

133
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:00,100
He just got a slight headache

134
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:01,060
You don't know that

135
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:03,340
I was scared to death at that time

136
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:06,020
But luckily, it's just a mistake

137
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:08,980
I was wondering why you looked upset

138
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:10,140
So that's the reason

139
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:11,900
Of course

140
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:14,500
If there was really something wrong with him

141
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:17,420
