142
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:22,500
Zhuzi, though it already passed

143
00:12:22,740 --> 00:12:23,860
But I'm still angry with you

144
00:12:24,340 --> 00:12:27,220
You tell me lots of trifles all the time

145
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:29,260
But why don't you tell me when something really important happened?

146
00:12:29,420 --> 00:12:30,220
What's wrong with you?

147
00:12:30,380 --> 00:12:33,020
I was in a panic

148
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:35,340
and didn't know what to do at that time

149
00:12:37,220 --> 00:12:38,340
You are a grown girl

150
00:12:38,860 --> 00:12:39,980
Please forgive me

151
00:12:40,940 --> 00:12:41,580
It's my fault

152
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:43,100
Please forgive me, it won't happen again

153
00:12:43,100 --> 00:12:48,220
For your baby girl or baby boy's sake

154
00:12:48,460 --> 00:12:49,380
I forgive you this time

155
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:51,500
How kind you are

156
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:52,300
Of course

157
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:54,740
What about you?

158
00:12:56,420 --> 00:13:02,780
Lin Sen told me that he and Xiang Zeyi both proposed to you

159
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:04,820
What do you think?

160
00:13:08,780 --> 00:13:11,900
I thought Lin Sen got no chances at all

161
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:14,780
Never expected that he would take such an action

162
00:13:16,180 --> 00:13:18,260
He is good

163
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:21,700
He had kept silent for too long

164
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:24,340
Finally he burst out

165
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:25,780
and one shot it

166
00:13:29,260 --> 00:13:30,500
So here is a problem

167
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:35,020
If nothing happened to Xiang Zeyi at that time

168
00:13:35,700 --> 00:13:38,340
you two may be living a happy life together now

169
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:42,340
And if Lin Sen wasn't too restrained

170
00:13:42,540 --> 00:13:43,980
maybe you two were a couple now

171
00:13:44,940 --> 00:13:46,380
You done?

172
00:13:47,020 --> 00:13:47,700
Yeah

173
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:54,100
You

174
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:56,260
You are being a mother now, stop gossiping

175
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:57,220
You know I'm being a mother

176
00:13:57,420 --> 00:13:58,180
So watch your hands

177
00:14:04,820 --> 00:14:09,500
The baby wants to know about it

178
00:14:10,580 --> 00:14:11,700
Tell me

179
00:14:11,940 --> 00:14:13,300
Who will you choose?

180
00:14:15,820 --> 00:14:17,940
You have talked about so many ifs just now

181
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:20,820
But you know

182
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:23,540
There are no ifs in life

183
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:27,580
What we can do is to try our best to be ourselves

184
00:14:32,260 --> 00:14:34,900
This is money I have earned by playing games for these years

185
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:39,260
Maybe I'm a childish guy in your mind

186
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:41,220
But I want to let you know

187
00:14:41,940 --> 00:14:42,740
All these years

188
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:45,300
I'm always longing to do something for you

189
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:47,500
I didn't take it out before

190
00:14:47,860 --> 00:14:50,580
because I thought it wasn't enough money

191
00:14:51,820 --> 00:14:54,460
But now I think it's time

192
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:57,180
Since it's about your dream

193
00:14:58,020 --> 00:15:00,780
I will certainly help you no matter how much money I have got

194
00:15:14,980 --> 00:15:17,220
I will work very harder

195
00:15:17,940 --> 00:15:19,060
and provide you a better life

196
00:15:23,620 --> 00:15:24,220
Daniao

197
00:15:27,540 --> 00:15:28,140
Thank you

198
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:34,140
You're welcome, darling

199
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:06,540
Only this box?

200
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:09,140
They have already moved other stuffs

201
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:10,300
Let's go

202
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:22,660
Don't do it

203
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:23,440
Don't

204
00:16:23,580 --> 00:16:24,080
Zhang Daniao

205
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,140
Wedding needs to have balloons

206
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:27,440
Yezi

207
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:29,160
Here you are

208
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:31,940
Daniao, please put these things at the back

209
00:16:32,100 --> 00:16:32,900
We still have time

210
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:33,760
Ok

211
00:16:36,700 --> 00:16:37,820
You are so early being here

212
00:16:39,780 --> 00:16:42,220
How do you think of putting these two together?

213
00:16:43,460 --> 00:16:44,380
Get some more

214
00:16:45,060 --> 00:16:45,820
Put it over there

215
00:16:45,980 --> 00:16:46,500
Right

216
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:47,540
What a big one

217
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:57,660
hey

218
00:17:11,740 --> 00:17:13,820
Zhuzi, let me help you

219
00:17:13,980 --> 00:17:15,500
Ok, we can deal with the balloons

220
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:16,200
Bye

221
00:17:22,060 --> 00:17:24,900
Well, how are the other things going?

222
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:26,340
Almost done

223
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:27,940
How do you think of it?

224
00:17:30,140 --> 00:17:30,860
Pretty good

225
00:17:31,060 --> 00:17:32,380
Your father's style

226
00:17:34,180 --> 00:17:35,980
It sounds like you know my father very much

227
00:17:38,060 --> 00:17:38,620
I do

228
00:17:40,220 --> 00:17:44,100
Your father chatted a lot with me recently

229
00:17:46,220 --> 00:17:48,020
It definitely is my father's style

230
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:02,620
That is it

231
00:18:43,660 --> 00:18:44,160
Come

232
00:18:44,580 --> 00:18:45,540
What are you doing?

233
00:18:45,700 --> 00:18:46,340
Have a look

234
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:49,500
What are you doing? So many people here

235
00:18:49,660 --> 00:18:51,140
It doesn't matter

236
00:18:51,300 --> 00:18:52,580
Please, please

237
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:53,660
We are already here

238
00:18:53,860 --> 00:18:55,900
Come, I'm here with you

239
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:00,220
It's ok, it's ok

240
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:17,740
What are you doing here?

241
00:19:25,780 --> 00:19:30,180
Lots of things didn't get popular when we were young

242
00:19:31,820 --> 00:19:34,420
Such as flowers, wedding

243
00:19:35,060 --> 00:19:37,660
and words I'm going to say

244
00:19:40,100 --> 00:19:40,820
Stop it

245
00:19:41,460 --> 00:19:42,340
Stop it

246
00:19:42,980 --> 00:19:46,460
I was learning how to surf the Internet recently

247
00:19:47,340 --> 00:19:49,940
And then I saw one word on Micro-blog

248
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:54,940
It reads that a couple change with the way they call each other

249
00:19:56,540 --> 00:19:59,140
Before getting married, they call each other's nickname

250
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:03,220
After getting married, they call each other darling

251
00:20:04,140 --> 00:20:08,300
And after having a baby, it turns into mom or dad

252
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:12,060
And then after getting old, it's old lady or old man

253
00:20:14,820 --> 00:20:20,460
When a man calls a woman he loves old lady

254
00:20:21,020 --> 00:20:25,620
it means that he has loved this woman for his whole life

255
00:20:30,620 --> 00:20:34,220
I don't know what so-called romance is

256
00:20:36,100 --> 00:20:37,980
as well as love

257
00:20:39,260 --> 00:20:40,340
The only thing I know is that

258
00:20:41,620 --> 00:20:43,060
when I first saw you

259
00:20:44,780 --> 00:20:47,900
you were doomed to me my wife

260
00:20:50,300 --> 00:20:51,300
my children's mother

261
00:20:54,620 --> 00:20:55,860
and my old lady

262
00:21:02,460 --> 00:21:05,980
Actually life is short

263
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:08,140
pretty short

264
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:11,500
But it will be enough with you by my side

265
00:21:14,300 --> 00:21:17,500
when I cry or laugh

266
00:21:19,100 --> 00:21:20,300
I'm satisfied with it

267
00:22:37,660 --> 00:22:41,820
I thought that people at their age knew nothing about love

268
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:44,500
All they know is how to live an ordinary life

269
00:22:45,660 --> 00:22:48,780
Now I think that the way they live a life together is really romantic

270
00:22:50,380 --> 00:22:52,580
Yeah, just as your father said

271
00:22:53,340 --> 00:22:58,340
The person you cry and laugh with in your life is the one you need

272
00:23:08,940 --> 00:23:11,140
Thank you for giving me such a good advice

273
00:23:12,660 --> 00:23:13,660
You're welcome

274
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:20,020
I found this boy looks really familiar

275
00:23:21,420 --> 00:23:23,940
And he is also a really good boy

276
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,820
I will tell Yezi about it

277
00:23:30,660 --> 00:23:34,620
You don't need to. Something is better to be kept just in mind

278
00:23:41,620 --> 00:23:45,980
Actually I really want you to be happy

279
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:50,380
and hope that your wish on the note will come true

280
00:25:00,860 --> 00:25:08,540
How I want to get old with you

281
00:25:10,580 --> 00:25:13,060
Just like your parents did

282
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:24,460
Yezi

283
00:25:39,700 --> 00:25:40,820
Will you marry me?

284
00:25:45,500 --> 00:25:47,740
Do you remember the first time we met?

285
00:25:52,860 --> 00:25:54,420
When I first saw you

286
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:59,580
you were painting confidently in a studio

287
00:26:03,060 --> 00:26:08,420
You were confident, outgoing, optimistic and funny

288
00:26:10,580 --> 00:26:12,580
During the time you disappeared

289
00:26:13,460 --> 00:26:16,420
I usually thought of a guy painting in the sun

290
00:26:20,220 --> 00:26:20,900
That guy

291
00:26:25,780 --> 00:26:27,140
It was long ago

292
00:26:30,820 --> 00:26:34,020
I used to try my best to stop loving you

293
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:39,940
But every time when I almost made it

294
00:26:42,140 --> 00:26:44,660
that guy in my mind would appear again

295
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:52,060
Then I found that maybe I could never forget you in my life

296
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,900
I could never stop loving you

297
00:26:57,780 --> 00:27:02,020
You said that things happened all these years made you change

298
00:27:04,940 --> 00:27:06,860
But even without these things

299
00:27:08,620 --> 00:27:10,580
we would still change, right?

300
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:22,340
You are right

301
00:27:24,980 --> 00:27:26,260
We would change

302
00:27:28,220 --> 00:27:34,820
I was always wondering if we could go back to that day

303
00:27:36,820 --> 00:27:38,420
And nothing bad happened

304
00:27:41,820 --> 00:27:45,980
Then we may not change

305
00:27:52,620 --> 00:27:53,740
and were really happy now

306
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:09,380
Time made people change

307
00:28:11,180 --> 00:28:14,620
But during that changing, we grew up

308
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:18,340
So we shouldn't be afraid of changing

309
00:28:19,580 --> 00:28:21,100
Instead we should feel grateful

310
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:25,220
For it made us know ourselves clearly

311
00:28:26,380 --> 00:28:28,180
and turned us into better people

312
00:28:29,300 --> 00:28:31,020
We also learnt how to love through it

313
00:28:33,340 --> 00:28:34,300
There was a time

314
00:28:37,180 --> 00:28:38,660
I didn't know how to face you

315
00:28:42,420 --> 00:28:45,180
Because I hurt so many people around me

316
00:28:48,820 --> 00:28:51,140
But actually the one I dared not face is myself

317
00:28:53,700 --> 00:28:55,100
I dared not face my change

318
00:28:57,540 --> 00:29:02,620
However, I forgot that future is the most important

319
00:29:16,220 --> 00:29:18,420
When you weren't around me

320
00:29:20,100 --> 00:29:22,100
I envied Zhuzi and Xinrang a lot

321
00:29:23,980 --> 00:29:29,820
Because they could always stay with people they love

322
00:29:34,340 --> 00:29:38,820
I also blamed god for being unfair to me

323
00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:45,180
Because it took my happiness away

324
00:29:47,940 --> 00:29:52,100
But later I found that real love

325
00:29:53,860 --> 00:29:56,980
Doesn't mean that we should stay together every second

326
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:02,820
but makes us into better people

327
00:30:34,020 --> 00:30:38,740
I thought I should say sorry to you

328
00:30:41,140 --> 00:30:46,540
Now I know it should be thank you

329
00:30:48,580 --> 00:30:51,580
Thank you for letting me know what a real love is

330
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:55,620
I kept you wait for me for so many years

331
00:30:57,860 --> 00:30:58,980
Now it's my turn

332
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:07,340
When we become people that could be trusted and depended on

333
00:31:08,700 --> 00:31:10,540
I will put this ring to your finger by myself

334
00:31:30,980 --> 00:31:34,300
This bracelet is very important to me

335
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:37,260
just like you

336
00:32:16,180 --> 00:32:16,680
Yezi

337
00:32:20,780 --> 00:32:21,380
How do you do

338
00:32:23,260 --> 00:32:24,060
I'm Xiang Zeyi
